item.title: CVE-2023-2337|2024-08-02T06:19:14.937Z -- unknown -- convertkit
item.description: The ConvertKit WordPress plugin before 2.2.1 does not escape a parameter before outputting it back in an attribute, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
